Document: GodotInstance
Path: godot/classes/class_godotinstance.rst
Summary: Methods related to focus management, pause/resume operations, and startup lifecycle for GodotInstance.

void: focus_in() Notifies the instance that it is now in focus.
void: focus_out() Notifies the instance that it is now not in focus.
bool: is_started() Returns true if this instance has been fully started.
bool: iteration() Runs a single iteration of the main loop. Returns true if the engine is attempting to quit.
void: pause() Notifies the instance that it is going to be paused.
void: resume() Notifies the instance that it is being resumed.
bool: start() Finishes this instance's startup sequence. Returns true on success.